KUrPh'aY LYShUr'aL VNGLH 'yVN 'aPhUrYM VUr'yVTh ShMUrVN KY Ph'yLV ShQUr VGNB YBV'a PhShT GDVD BChVTSh.
VBL-Y'aMUrV LLBBM KL-Ur'yThM ZKUrThY 'yThH SBBVM M'yLLYHM NGD PhNY HYV.
BUr'yThM YShMChV-MLK VBKChShYHM ShUrYM.
KLM MN'aPhYM KMV ThNVUr B'yUrH M'aPhH YShBVTh M'yYUr MLVSh BTShQ 'yD-ChMTShThV.
YVM MLKNV HChLV ShUrYM ChMTh MYYN MShK YDV 'aTh-LTShTShYM.
KY-QUrBV KThNVUr LBM B'aUrBM KL-HLYLH YShN 'aPhHM BQUr HV'a B'yUr K'aSh LHBH.
KLM YChMV KThNVUr V'aKLV 'aTh-ShPhTYHM KL-MLKYHM NPhLV 'aYN-QUr'a BHM 'aLY.
'aPhUrYM B'yMYM HV'a YThBVLL 'aPhUrYM HYH 'yGH BLY HPhVKH.
'aKLV ZUrYM KChV VHV'a L'a YD'y GM-ShYBH ZUrQH BV VHV'a L'a YD'y.
V'yNH G'aVN-YShUr'aL BPhNYV VL'a-ShBV 'aL-YHVH 'aLHYHM VL'a BQShHV BKL- Z'aTh.
VYHY 'aPhUrYM KYVNH PhVThH 'aYN LB MTShUrYM QUr'aV 'aShVUr HLKV.
K'aShUr YLKV 'aPhUrVSh 'yLYHM UrShThY K'yVPh HShMYM 'aVUrYDM 'aYSUrM KShM'y L'yDThM.
'aVY LHM KY-NDDV MMNY ShD LHM KY-PhSh'yV BY V'aNKY 'aPhDM VHMH DBUrV 'yLY KZBYM.
